  "answer": "Every feature service directly imports apiClient. If its method signatures change, all 5 service files break: authService (loginUser, logoutUser, getCurrentUser), discussionService (fetchDiscussions, createDiscussion), commentService (fetchComments, addComment), teamService (fetchTeams, createTeam), userService (fetchUser, updateUser). The UI components are indirectly affected because they call these service functions. The most critical path is authService.loginUser → LoginForm.handleSubmit since it is the only write-path currently wired into the UI alongside commentService.addComment → CommentForm.handleSubmit.",
